{"locales":{"en":{"GxzRg35XsK":{"lh_2w_title":"Shopify to RE NXT Connector","lh_6ocof5_title":"What is the Shopify to RE NXT Connector?","lh_axl7kz_content_html":"The connector is an app that transfers donor data from Shopify orders (product purchase or donation) directly into Blackbaud Raiser\u2019s Edge NXT.<!--lh-live-editor-->","lh_6ocrhe_title":"Why would I need this app?","lh_axl7ky_content_html":"If you are a non-profit or charity that runs an online or in person store using Shopify and want to have purchases easily transfer into your Blackbaud Raiser's Edge database this is the solution for you.<!--lh-live-editor-->","lh_6ocujn_title":"What do I need to use this?","lh_axl7kx_content_html":"To use this you would need:<div>- A Shopify Store<\/div><div>- A Blackbaud RE NXT account<\/div><div>- Willingness to learn&nbsp;<\/div><!--lh-live-editor-->","lh_6ocxlw_title":"Is there a cost?","lh_axl7kw_content_html":"Yes. There is an initial setup fee to get your organization connected ($1,000 CAD) and then a monthly fee of $50 CAD.<div><br><\/div><div>This cost helps to cover app updates, maintainence and our own costs to manage the servers that run the application.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Any additional profits would get invested back into Grand River Hospital to support health care in our region.<br><\/div><!--lh-live-editor-->","lh_6od0o5_title":"Is it the app secure?","lh_axl7kv_content_html":"Yes. The app does not store any donor data or personal information.&nbsp;<div><br><\/div><div>Additionally we (Grand River Hospital Foundation) cannot access your donor information and you cannot access ours.<br><\/div><!--lh-live-editor-->","lh_9e88hg_title":"What can this app do?","lh_u7m56g_content_html":"Transfers purchases in Shopify into Blackbaud Raiser\u2019s Edge NXT automatically as a gift on a batch and on a donor record.<div><br><\/div><div>Looks for duplicate records and adds new donors to Blackbaud Raiser\u2019s Edge NXT when necessary.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Updates donor addresses when an order is placed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Allows you to set default Campaign, Appeal and Fund on any product when importing into Blackbaud Raiser\u2019s Edge NXT. This can be customized on a per product and per product variant basis.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Allows you to see what product they purchased on the gift record in Blackbaud Raiser\u2019s Edge NXT and provides a reference back to finding the order in Shopify.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Allows you to track if the gift needs a receipt or not in Blackbaud Raiser\u2019s Edge NXT.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Provides an error message automatically to you if a gift cannot be added into RE making your life stress free.<\/div><!--lh-live-editor-->","lh_9e85f7_title":"Who are we?","lh_u7m56f_content_html":"<p>If you came to this page directly from another site such as Blackbaud Marketplace you might now know who we are.&nbsp;<br><\/p><p>Grand River Hospital Foundation&nbsp; raises funds to help Grand River Hospital provide exceptional health care.&nbsp;<\/p><p>With the support from generous donors and loyal community partnerships, Grand River Hospital Foundation is able to grant funds for medical equipment and technology; renovation projects; and local clinical and health research and education.&nbsp;<\/p><p>The commitment to health care in our region ensures that the residents of Waterloo Region and Guelph Wellington will have access to the best health care services close to home.<\/p><!--lh-live-editor-->"},"338qmuqt6lw":{"lh_8kwg_title":"Interested in learning more?","lh_8kwg_button":"Contact our Donor Innovation Director, Dan Lombardi"}}},"name":"Shopify to Blackbaud C"}
